text: Chesalles-sur-Moudon is a former municipality in the district Broye-Vully in the canton of Vaud in Switzerland. On 1 January 2017, it is part of the municipality of Lucens.Amtliches Gemeindeverzeichnis der Schweiz accessed 10 January 2017 == References == Category:Former municipalities of Vaud
title: Chesalles-sur-Moudon
